According to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vehicle_registration_plates_of_Ireland#Series_per_county_1903-1986" rel="nofollow">Wikipedia</a>: Dublin CC: IK 1 to IK 9999 (Dec 1903 - Mar 1927);

IK 9729 is very close to the end ot the series, has to be registered in 1926 or 27.

10,000 registrations in 24 years would be 416 per year, but presumably there were more in the later years, so just 270 off the final number is certainly after September 1926.
